No. 10-6470. Rickey Sabedra, Petitioner v. United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit. 562 U.S. 1039, 131 S. Ct. 627, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 8944.

178 L. Ed. 2d 431,

November 15, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied, and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
